operator over loading - when operator have different implementation depending on their arguments.
abstraction is the concept of hiding the complex details of how something works and only showing the essential features.  It's like  a simplified model of a complex system.
Think of it as focusing on what an object does rather than how it does it.

My understanding of Abstraction: So in general. An abstraction is a class that creates necessary methods that must be used when it's inherited in other class or other subclasses.